snippet.textDisplay:
Sound_Temp only worked on a few of the songs. They have gone through many other composers as the game developed.

 The game doesn't really suck either. It's the only MMO I've played where you don't need anything to do find fun. That kind of style eventually gets boring, but when you start playing other games, you'll understand that Ragnarok hit MMOs right on head with it's style. I don't play it anymore, because the game itself got pretty boring, but looking back on it, it's not that bad.
